{"tid":1509691,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果日報：共同檢控　兒童要上成人庭","createTime":"2019-08-27T02:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T06:53:02.000Z","uid":279895,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"32ef97189a9f2a0d61d5cf1ca81a6fd63722ae7b","tid":1509691,"uid":279895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190827/20756733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756733&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=cf0044f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190827%2F20756733&h=816b9858\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190827/20756733</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名12歲男童前日在荃葵青大遊行後被捕，根據法例規定，如年齡未滿14歲的兒童被檢控，須按照香港法例第226章《少年犯條例》（下稱條例）的條文處理，但條例中亦提及，針對一名兒童或少年人及一名年滿16歲的人而提出的共同檢控，仍須由具有簡易司法管轄權但非少年法庭的法庭聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>律師：13歲以下不得判監</strong><br />\n大律師潘展平表示，在前日荃葵青大遊行的衝突事件中，被捕人士有機會被視為共同檢控，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即使男童只得12歲，仍有機會被帶到成人法庭進行審訊，其中非法集結最高可判監5年。</span></strong>涉案男童亦有面對監禁的機會，視乎案情的嚴重性，不過法官一般會考慮讓少年被告改過自新的方法，優先以感化、判入教導所等刑罰處理。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄則表示，兒童一旦在成人法庭被定罪，有權選擇將案件交由少年法庭處理判罪；在兒童認罪的前提下，根據條例第15條（1）（a），法庭可行使酌情權採用撤銷控罪的方式處理案件。該條例指出，兒童（10至13歲）不得被判處監禁，法庭如要以褫奪自由來懲罰少年犯，可考慮判其入教導所、勞教中心或更生中心。另外，根據條例中刑事責任的年齡推定，10歲以下兒童毋須負上刑責。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：2019-08-27《蘋果日報》A04|要聞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ts66yLE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTs66yLE.jpg&h=046b6067&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcd7cddef436e4dd188cf1795af9a66e5c0ae423","tid":1509691,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=9a8cb351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=f38ce6fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrhPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=048c0b38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"838634aab4e525b41fb0810b63e046741fd3d5b7","tid":1509691,"uid":259329,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8024903f0a51485912eb7cde1081b93842f556cb","tid":1509691,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:35:50.000Z","msg":"求幫推<br />\n<br />\n最新post 睇得清楚d + 加左明天有義士再審係頂！(極正經)(請推至長期置頂)被捕義士進程，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1b02bcde9f50cf81e4ca94abed9d450acd5b16f","tid":1509691,"uid":21234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240baf8d52bc8ae6ab7dc9603274adce184e901e","tid":1509691,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:51:36.000Z","msg":"DLLM果日6點左右班狗已經跳車夾住班物資組唔比郁<br />\n跟住7:30 先話落叉要夾返狗竇,<br />\n告非法集結<br />\n<br />\n827 14:00 包圍港鐵總部大樓 要求回應停駛事件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dKqKDS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dKqKDS</a>